# Task 4 – Download the Dataset

## Project

Credit Card Approval Prediction Using Machine Learning

## Objective

Download the dataset required for building the machine learning model.

## Dataset Source

- Kaggle
- Credit Card Fraud Detection Dataset

## Dataset Link

https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud

## Dataset Information

- 284,807 transaction records
- 31 features
- Binary classification target
- Fraudulent and genuine transaction labels

## Steps Performed

1. Open Kaggle.
2. Search for the dataset.
3. Download the ZIP file.
4. Extract the dataset.
5. Store the CSV file in the project folder.

## Output

Dataset successfully downloaded and prepared for preprocessing.

## Conclusion

The dataset is successfully collected and is ready for data analysis, preprocessing, model training, and deployment.
